<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0 fontsize7">Motions for directed verdict abolished.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0 fontsize7">Motions for judgment of acquittal adopted; court may reserve decision; renewal, Rule 29.</p>
</note>
